lead_paragraph: WITCHEL--Sam, 91. Died February 27, 2016 in New Rochelle, NY. Beloved husband of Barbara Witchel, father of Alex Witchel, Gregory Witchel and Emmett Witchel. Brother of Marcia Babbitt. Predeceased by adored daughter, Phoebe Kahanov. Father-in-law to Frank Rich, Monica Witchel, Learan Kahanov and Danielle Adler Witchel. Funeral services private. 1/3
